{"serial": "40002", "department_serial": 47, "code": "MGT009", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Strategic Human Resource Management", "ch": "策略性人力資源管理"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": "[密集授課]日期：4/20、4/27、5/4、5/11、5/18、5/26(日)、6/1，0900-1745"}, "instructor": {"en": ["Chen, Chun-Hsi"], "ch": ["陳春希"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 6, "session": ["5", "6", "7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "I1", "room": "222"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "管理學院高階主管企管碩士班", "en": "Executive Master of Business Administration"}, "system": {"ch": "碩士在職專班", "en": "Master Programme (Adult Learning)"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 63, "remark": {"ch": "[密集授課]日期：4/20、4/27、5/4、5/11、5/18、5/26(日)、6/1，0900-1745", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程主要自組織發展的角度，以主題方式深入探討人力資源管理在組織中的策略性角色。有別於傳統人力資源管理中所強調，對組織員工選用育留的各項人力資源功能，策略性人力資源管理側重在關鍵性人才的管理與發展，讓人力資源管理能夠與組織策略的執行能夠銜接，充份發揮人力資源管理在組織中策略伙伴的角色。", "en": "“The course will explore the HR strategic role in an organization from the point of business development.  Comparing to traditional HR, the strategic role of HR in an organization will focus primarily on talent management and development.  The strategic HR will link people management to the business strategy and will help develop the role of strategic business partner in an organization.“"}, "outline": {"ch": "策略性人力資源管理基本概念\n組織結構設計理論與原則\n組織職務設計與人力資源規劃\n企業人才招募發展趨勢專題演講\n人力資源的發展及個案研討\n企業菁英人才管理與發展專題演講\n組織績效管理及個案研討\n組織績效管理專題演講\n策略性獎酬及個案研討\n人力資源的獎酬設計專題演講\n員工關係管理及個案研討\n勞資關係專題演講\n人力資源e 化管理及個案研討\n人力資源e 化管理專題演講", "en": "Basic concepts of strategic HR\nOrganizational structures and principles\nJob design and human resource planning\nInvited lecture on the topic of talent recruting and selection\nCase study in human resource development\nInvited lecture on the topic of on talent management and development\nCase study on organizational performance management\nInvited lecture on organizational performance management\nStrategic reward and case study\nThe design of strategci compensation\nEmployeed relation management and case study\nInvited lecture on the topic on labor relation.\ne-HR and case study\nInvited lecture on the topic of eHR"}, "textbook": {"ch": "“人力資源管理十二堂課(第四版)-天下文化出版\n人才管理大戰略 (第一版)-大寫出版社“", "en": "“人力資源管理十二堂課(第四版)-天下文化出版\n人才管理大戰略 (第一版)-大寫出版社“"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "0", "en": "0"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "專題報告 50％\n個案研討        50％", "en": "none"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "自行預約", "en": "by appointment"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "人力資源管理", "en": "人力資源管理"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "管理知識", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考和解決問題能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "國際觀", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "社會責任", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "溝通能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Management Knowledge", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)"]}, {"competencies": "Critical Thinking and Problem-solving", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Global Perspective", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Social Responsibility", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Communication Skill", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}]}, "assignCriteria": {"ch": ["系所:限管理學院